### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Signup
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "fullName": "Alex Mercer",
  "email": "alex@example.com",
  "password": "Secret123!"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alex@example.com",
  "password": "Secret123!"
}

### Session check (paste your token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN

### Track event (new)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T08:00:00+05:30",
  "location": "home",
  "destination": "office",
  "action": "leave for work",
  "note": "weekday commute"
}

### Track event (compat route)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/habits/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T08:05:00+05:30",
  "location": "home",
  "destination": "office",
  "action": "leave for work"
}

### Get reminder (new)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reminder?userId=alex&currentLocation=home

### Get reminder (compat route)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reminders?userId=alex&currentLocation=home

### Chat
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T08:10:00+05:30",
  "currentLocation": "home",
  "message": "What should I do now?"
}

### Assistant check-in question
GET http://localhost:3000/api/assistant/question

### Assistant check-in answer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/assistant/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotKey": "2026-03-13:08",
  "questionId": "q_location_now",
  "questionText": "Where are you right now?",
  "selectedOption": "Home",
  "answer": "Home"
}

### Location update
POST http://localhost:3000/api/location/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 12.9716,
  "longitude": 77.5946,
  "source": "manual",
  "label": "Office"
}

### Frequent places
GET http://localhost:3000/api/location/frequent-places?minVisits=3

### Daily insight
GET http://localhost:3000/api/assistant/daily-insight

### Calendar upcoming (via MuleSoft)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/integrations/calendar/upcoming?limit=5

### Weather (via MuleSoft)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/integrations/weather/current?location=Bengaluru
